What's wrong with this picture?

00:19:08.750 --> 00:19:09.670
I'm not in it.

00:19:09.670 --> 00:19:10.990
Well, that's a good one.

00:19:10.990 --> 00:19:12.670
Oh, I bought it at a US clothing shop.

00:19:12.670 --> 00:19:13.630
