00:24:42.920 --> 00:24:44.960
Oh, he will be so proud of you, Marshall.

00:24:44.960 --> 00:24:46.360
Yeah.

00:24:46.360 --> 00:24:48.720
Isn't it time you two took a break?

00:24:48.720 --> 00:24:50.000
Deadline's a deadline, Mom.

00:24:50.000 --> 00:24:51.840
Well, don't work too hard.

00:24:51.840 --> 00:24:53.600
And if you get hungry, there's some soy pilaf

